      "updated": 1769462841261,
      "link": null,
      "locked": false,
      "fontSize": 14,
      "fontFamily": 1,
      "text": "Key Relationships:\n\n• Material entities have ports\n• Ports connect via flowsTo\n• Components have upstream/\n  downstream relationships\n• Sensors monitor ports (SOSA)\n• Observations measure qualities\n• Samples taken at sampling points\n• Compliance checks observations\n  against requirements\n• Models represent entities\n• Models have capabilities\n• Variables link to ports",
      "textAlign": "left",
      "verticalAlign": "top",
      "containerId": null,
      "originalText": "Key Relationships:\n\n• Material entities have ports\n• Ports connect via flowsTo\n• Components have upstream/\n  downstream relationships\n• Sensors monitor ports (SOSA)\n• Observations measure qualities\n• Samples taken at sampling points\n• Compliance checks observations\n  against requirements\n• Models represent entities\n• Models have capabilities\n• Variables link to ports",
      "lineHeight": 1.25,
      "index": "aj",
      "autoResize": true
    },
