      "updated": 1769462841261,
      "link": null,
      "locked": false,
      "fontSize": 14,
      "fontFamily": 1,
      "text": "Design Principles:\n\n✓ BFO-grounded: All classes align with\n  Basic Formal Ontology upper level\n\n✓ Modular: Separate concerns into\n  independent, reusable modules\n\n✓ Port-based topology: Following\n  OntoCAPE pattern for flow networks\n\n✓ Entity-Feature-Value: Manchester ODP\n  for observations and measurements\n\n✓ Multi-jurisdiction: Supports any\n  regulatory framework (EU, US, WHO)\n\n✓ Interoperable: Bridges to SOSA/SSN,\n  PROV-O, QUDT for semantic web\n\n✓ Optimization-ready: Decision variables\n  and model capabilities for agents",
      "textAlign": "left",
      "verticalAlign": "top",
      "containerId": null,
      "originalText": "Design Principles:\n\n✓ BFO-grounded: All classes align with\n  Basic Formal Ontology upper level\n\n✓ Modular: Separate concerns into\n  independent, reusable modules\n\n✓ Port-based topology: Following\n  OntoCAPE pattern for flow networks\n\n✓ Entity-Feature-Value: Manchester ODP\n  for observations and measurements\n\n✓ Multi-jurisdiction: Supports any\n  regulatory framework (EU, US, WHO)\n\n✓ Interoperable: Bridges to SOSA/SSN,\n  PROV-O, QUDT for semantic web\n\n✓ Optimization-ready: Decision variables\n  and model capabilities for agents",
      "lineHeight": 1.25,
      "index": "ak",
