      "fontSize": 14,
      "fontFamily": 1,
      "text": "Module Dependencies:\n\nwaterframe.ttl (main)\n├─ imports core/material_entities\n├─ imports core/properties\n├─ imports information\n├─ imports capabilities\n├─ imports qualities\n├─ imports sampling\n├─ imports compliance\n└─ imports bridges/sosa_alignment\n\ninfo → material_entities\ncapabilities → material_entities, information\nqualities → material_entities\nsampling → material_entities\ncompliance → qualities, sampling\nsosa_alignment → qualities",
      "textAlign": "left",
      "verticalAlign": "top",
      "containerId": null,
      "originalText": "Module Dependencies:\n\nwaterframe.ttl (main)\n├─ imports core/material_entities\n├─ imports core/properties\n├─ imports information\n├─ imports capabilities\n├─ imports qualities\n├─ imports sampling\n├─ imports compliance\n└─ imports bridges/sosa_alignment\n\ninfo → material_entities\ncapabilities → material_entities, information\nqualities → material_entities\nsampling → material_entities\ncompliance → qualities, sampling\nsosa_alignment → qualities",
